{"tid":2325842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國今次好大機會內戰，有冇人買定水麵午餐肉存貨？","createTime":"2020-12-15T01:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T02:05:01.000Z","uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fc51dcf714ece3e42b875e382c966d8f675f35b6","tid":2325842,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T01:46:50.000Z","msg":"美國內戰又好,中美開戰又好,侵侵反 cup 又好,有咩事發生都唔驚,,要鳩縮唔出街都實有得食~~<br />\n當然,,到有日真係出現 全香港範圍MAP炮 就咩都唔使講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i62.photobucket.com/albums/h85/devillam/20110924276.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi62.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh85%2Fdevillam%2F20110924276.jpg&h=0447ef5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放在廚房櫃的鑵頭同米,[現鑵頭總存貨有$10000左右]米有50kg<br />\n由歐洲火腿,到中國午餐肉,回煱肉,,豆,菜,金寶湯<br />\n<img src=\"http://i62.photobucket.com/albums/h85/devillam/20110924275.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi62.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh85%2Fdevillam%2F20110924275.jpg&h=8ac8e8b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一箱箱未開太多,,放到出廳[依d全部係魚]<br />\n<img src=\"http://i62.photobucket.com/albums/h85/devillam/20110924274.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi62.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh85%2Fdevillam%2F20110924274.jpg&h=4662e826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n水污染,未驚~~~現有16箱 1.5L X12<br />\n其實一向飲樽裝水好耐,現在D水喉水煮完都飲到唔舒服<br />\n即食面 有 5箱左右啦<br />\n<br />\n另外,,打邊爐石油氣有存貨 21支,,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n來吧~~~<br />\n大混亂~~~<br />\n美國內戰吧~~~<br />\n無水~~無電~~無野買的日子呀~~~<br />\n<br />\n期待,手持午餐肉就可以有大波鬼妹屌的日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a51d2e2612138cf408a28c7cf1ce7707b67ebee","tid":2325842,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T01:49:37.000Z","